        <h1>Child of Everything</h1>
        <p>To the mother,</p>
        <p>The creation,</p>
        <p>The disruption.</p>

        <p>To the father,</p>
        <p>The structure,</p>
        <p>The control.</p>

        <p>I’m your child.</p>
        <p>I’m life,</p>
        <p>I’m a human soul.</p>

        <p>Now I breathe,</p>
        <p>Like waves,</p>
        <p>Like the sun.</p>

        <p>Can you teach me again,</p>
        <p>How to laugh, cry, play, and run?</p>

        <p>I see you now,</p>
        <p>My search ended here.</p>

        <p>Now I stand,</p>
        <p>On my own ground.</p>

        <p>Take my body,</p>
        <p>Expand it a home.</p>

        <p>In this endless journey,</p>
        <p>There’s a game of life,</p>

        <p>we stay.</p>
        <p>we play.</p>

        <p>we meet,</p>
        <p>again and again.</p>

        <p>Like the star explode into novae,</p>
        <p>Light her way home.</p>

        <div class="signature">— Nova Zhang</div>
